        <string>dlgTeleportTo(8, 236, 0, W);</string>
        <string>dlgTeleportTo(7, 236, 0, E, 2055);</string>
        <string>useCameraBookmark(Quest_HD1_03);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>「明日&lt;da/yo&gt;、ソフラーブ博士、今夜上手く事が運べばだ&lt;ga/kedo&gt;」</text>
